Control Flow Test.

This recipe has a method call and a double loop. It's a bit of a hardcoded
cheat, really.

Ingredients.
6 aubergine
32 ml soy sauce
61 dashes tabasco sauce

Method.
Put aubergine into the 2nd mixing bowl.
Put tabasco sauce into the 2nd mixing bowl.
Put soy sauce into the 2nd mixing bowl.
Serve with Soy Sauce Glaze.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.
Pour contents of the 2nd mixing bowl into the 2nd baking dish.

Serves 2.

Soy Sauce Glaze.

Ingredients.
1 aubergine
3 spring onions
3 g noodles
32 ml soy sauce
42 dashes tabasco sauce

Method.
Cook the noodles.
  Put noodles into the mixing bowl.
  Put spring onions into the mixing bowl.
  Remove aubergine from the mixing bowl.
  Fold spring onions into the mixing bowl.
  Cook the spring onions.
    Put tabasco sauce into the mixing bowl.
    Put soy sauce into the mixing bowl.
    Set aside.
  Heat until cooked.
Heat the noodles until cooked.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.
